{"tid":481050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日化妝品專營店貼告示禁中國人入內　網民又搬「要不是中國論」洗板","createTime":"2017-11-26T18:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T03:07:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"70a96841c994362e5f30c825ae456e1a1f271363","tid":481050,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T18:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/26194538/image1511696732742.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F26194538%2Fimage1511696732742.png&h=006497df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李小龍的《精武門》中，上海租界公園掛上「華人與狗不得入內」的告示牌，氣得李小龍飾演的陳真一腳踢爛告示牌，而日本愛知縣近日亦有類似的告示牌，沒惹來真人版陳真上門，但被中國網友轟炸洗板，總公司亦急撤告示兼道歉。<br />\n<br />\n事發在日本四大化妝品品牌之一的POLA，其位於愛知縣半田市乙川的專營店，上周五（24日）被網民發現貼出「中國人禁止入內」的告示。網民在微博分享相片時，亦不忘發表「要不是中國論」，指「POLA公司這幾年收益突飛猛漲，完全得益中國市場迅速發展」，其他網民亦批評POLA此舉形同過橋抽板、不尊重客戶，更指有「多家在日華人企業、華人POLA代理個人投訴到POLA總部，要求改正錯誤道歉」。<br />\n<br />\nPOLA總部復在官網貼道歉聲明，就事件引起的不快和困擾致歉，並已確認涉事的專營店已撕走相關告示，但同時指，從涉事店舖所得的信息，與部份網絡流的有出入，惟聲明未有說明出入之處為何。雖POLA已即時行動，道歉及撤聲明，但玻璃心已碎的廣大中國網民看來尚未能平息怒火，聲言罷買罷採購，且看後來發展如何。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/236168/%E6%97%A5%E5%8C%96%E5%A6%9D%E5%93%81%E5%B0%88%E7%87%9F%E5%BA%97%E8%B2%BC%E5%91%8A%E7%A4%BA%E7%A6%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%85%A7%E3%80%80%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%88%E6%90%AC%E3%80%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F236168%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%25A6%259D%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%25B0%2588%25E7%2587%259F%25E5%25BA%2597%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%2585%25A7%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258F%2588%25E6%2590%25AC%25E3%2580%258C%2F&d=xaBMCAPEdhMBgXjUKYuXTG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=170011cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/236168/%E6%97%A5%E5%8C%96%E5%A6%9D%E5%93%81%E5%B0%88%E7%87%9F%E5%BA%97%E8%B2%BC%E5%91%8A%E7%A4%BA%E7%A6%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%85%A7%E3%80%80%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%88%E6%90%AC%E3%80%8C/</a>"},{"pid":"1d2044c41fbe211a322f3d71ac416fa7f2b93bc3","tid":481050,"uid":47080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T18:15:35.000Z","msg":"好肯定去到日本會見到大量中國人一袋袋咁掃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45861ce95635d228c38114383b4211ac80599c41","tid":481050,"uid":45368,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T18:22:16.000Z","msg":"好彩日本人識分香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6000164c8d6549236e89697c090d5e35a5c3ba0","tid":481050,"uid":142325,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T18:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩日本人識分香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你肯定？香港人又好好咩？去親原宿porter 都見到d香港人大大聲喺入面試袋，好醜"},{"pid":"9f4790906d5da2c7b9905c9d51cb6f43068dfe5e","tid":481050,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T23:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩日本人識分香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219cd27e542f408e28d8c60ed39117b1c3794cea","tid":481050,"uid":1914,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T23:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩日本人識分香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一時時其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申直情比人當架仔"},{"pid":"f7f83899d156cd03943b60705054c2a52d348249","tid":481050,"uid":139139,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T23:18:50.000Z","msg":"去咗日本無人當我係中國人點解？<br />\n但係佢又唔俾我入女僕咖啡室，淨係比本地人。<br />\n咁究竟佢當我係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f413ecc84de5774c37297ed975e13c226835b6","tid"